#React Movie App
This is a simple React app for searching, adding and managing movies. It includes the following components:

Login: a form for users to log in with their email and password
MovieForm: a form for users to add a new movie with a title and year
MyMovies: a component for displaying a list of the user's movies with options to edit or delete each movie
SearchMovie: a component for searching and displaying movie results from the OMDb API
Installation
To run this app locally, follow these steps:

Clone this repository
Install dependencies with npm install
Start the app with npm start
Open your browser and navigate to http://localhost:3000
Usage
Once the app is running, you can use the different components to search, add and manage movies.

Login
The Login component allows users to log in with their email and password. Once logged in, the user can access the MyMovies component.

MovieForm
The MovieForm component allows users to add a new movie with a title and year. Once added, the movie will appear in the MyMovies component.

MyMovies
The MyMovies component displays a list of the user's movies with options to edit or delete each movie.

SearchMovie
The SearchMovie component allows users to search for movies using the OMDb API. Search results will be displayed in a list of movie cards.

